<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.9.6">
<l>maṉṉāy nīrerikāl mañculāvumā kācamumām</l>
<l>puṇṇā rākkaitaṉṉuḷ pulampittaḷarn teyttoḻintēṉ</l>
<l>viṇṇār nīḷcikara viraiyārttiru vēṅkaṭavā</l>
<l>vaṇṇā vantaṭaintē ṉaṭiyēṉaiyāṭ koṇṭaruḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lamenting [and] languishing, I withered and weakened,</l>
<l rend="indent">[caught] in a scar-filled body</l>
<l>That is of earth, water, fire, wind, and cloud-shifting ether;</l>
<l>You of Tiruvēṅkaṭam full of fragrance with peaks</l>
<l rend="indent">whose high summits fill the heavens,</l>
<l>I came [here and] took refuge;</l>
<l rend="indent">be gracious, receiving me, your servant, in service.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
